  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The mean score of 8 players in a basketball game was 14.5 points. If the highest individual score is removed, the mean score of the remaining 7 players becomes 12 points. What was the highest score?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p>20</p>\n"
